wondering what she was going to do with Megatrons
rubber ducky from the original Beast Wars.

--- cardhead649 <cardhead649@...> wrote:
> The loading job is quickly finished; Gatara notices
> a bit of extra 
> room and slides in a smaller box without paying much
> attention to 
> what's in it - she knows the parts she's getting
> from this deal are 
> going to be more than enough to get the job done.
> 
> "Get this junker moving," she tells Flicker.  "I'll
> follow you in the 
> air."  She's not interested in taking unneccessary
> chances, even 
> though she expects the Predacon won't dare misbehave
> with Phoenix's 
> well-being in the balance.
